title: {Godprop #13} Yomopu Deposit Fee Handling
body:
If this proposal passes:

The DAO will handle these assets accordingly:
1. DAI - Deposited into Cream. (as per prop 11 if it passes)
2. SPIRIT - Vaulted on mlnl.finance
3. BOO - Vaulted on mlnl.finance
4. ORI - Converted to MECHS farming AURORA on hyperjump
5. ZOO - held
6. CHAD - Vaulted on grim

Each proposal for a new yomopu pool, going forward, should specify where the deposit fee should be vaulted. (This only pertains to yomopu as Acres has no deposit fees)

These Will Be the Options for Deposit Fee Handling
1. Cream
2. Grim.finance (single tokens only)
3. Reaper.farm (single tokens only)
4. mlnl.finance (single tokens only)
5. allocated towards, in some manner, farming on spirit, spooky, hyper, waka, paintswap, or sponsored zoo farms
6. allocated to purchasing ECHO and burning it.
7. allocated to purchasing gDELI and burning it.
8. allocated towards farming acres
9. burned
